<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width,initial-scale=1">
  <title>Cookie Policy — SourcemAI</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/theme.css">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/app.css">
</head>
<body class="legal-page">
  <header class="legal-header"><a href="/" class="brand">SourcemAI</a></header>
  <main class="legal-main">
    <h1>Cookie Policy</h1>
    <p class="muted">Last updated: <%= lastUpdated %></p>
    <p>SourcemAI uses cookies in three categories:</p>
    <h2>1. Essential cookies</h2><p>The session cookie used to keep you signed in is essential and is set regardless of consent. It expires when you log out or after 7 days. We also use a CSRF-protection cookie (HttpOnly, Lax).</p>
    <h2>2. Analytics cookies</h2><p>Only set after you accept the cookie banner. Used in aggregate to improve the service. Disabled by default and never used to identify individual users.</p>
    <h2>3. Marketing cookies</h2><p>SourcemAI does not set marketing cookies. We do not run advertising trackers.</p>
    <p>You can change your choice at any time from the cookie banner.</p>
  </main>
</body>
</html>
